HEADWORD: Wallaroo
<hw>Wal`la*roo"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any one of several species of kangaroos of the genus
<gen>Macropus</gen>, especially <spn>Macropus robustus</spn>, sometimes
called the <stype>great wallaroo</stype>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wallbird</ent>⟦br⟧
